    "Library preparation and sequencing was performed as a service by Novogene.",
    "Library construction and RNA sequencing.",
    "Seedlings of Ae.",
    "tauschii accessions TA10171, TA1675 and TA2576 were raised as 5-6 seeds per pot (6 × 6 × 10 cm) in a growth chamber at 22-24 °C under long-day photoperiods of 16/8 h day/night cycle with high-output white-fluorescent tubes until the third leaf stage (about 2-3 weeks old), and then transferred to a 4 °C growth chamber with a long-day photoperiod for vernalization.",
    "After a nine-week vernalization period, all the plants were moved back to the original growth chamber under the controlled conditions mentioned above."
